      "name": "Transition — Pre-awakening ➔ Awakening",
      "type": "transition",
      "icons": [],
      "sequences": [],
      "rows": [
        { "input": "QUICKSLOT", "protected": "Iframe into SA" },
        { "input": "C", "protected": "FG" },
        { "input": "W+RMB", "protected": "—" },
        { "input": "A/D+RMB ➔ SPACE", "protected": "Iframe" },
        { "input": "W+LMB (Block) ➔ SPACE", "protected": "FG" },
        { "input": "SHIFT+ANY ➔ SPACE", "protected": "SA+FG" },
        { "input": "A/D+LMB ➔ SPACE", "protected": "—" },
        { "input": "Q ➔ SPACE", "protected": "SA+FG" }
      ],
      "notes": [
        "Notable skills to use before Promptness to swap into awakening (the ➔ SPACE rows).",
        "Pre-awak Q + Space ➔ Q: sit in pre-awakening block holding SPACE and tapping Q — Promptness out of the block-removal animation. Fully protected as long as Promptness is off cd."
      ],
      "comment": "W+LMB (Block) ➔ SPACE: has to be in pre-awakening block.",
      "video": null
    },
